Reviewed-by: Tzung-Bi Shih <tzungbi@kernel.org>
Tested-by: Tom Vincent <linux@tlvince.com>
Link: https://lore.kernel.org/r/20250521-cros-ec-mfd-chctl-probe-v1-1-6ebfe3a6efa7@weissschuh.net
